data.description: Beautiful 2 family house in the desirable Bergen Lafayette section of Jersey City. Second floor is a 2 bed 1 bath apartment. First floor is a 2 bed 1 bath with access to a large full and finish basement and a backyard. This is the perfect opportunity for owner occupants looking for some rental income or for investors. This property is close to Garfield Avenue Light Rail Station, buses, shopping, schools, houses of worship,  Berry Lane Park. Don't let this opportunity pass you by. 1st floor lease is ends July 30th,2024 2nfl lease expires April 30th,2024  property is sold as is.
